FBIS4-5937 "dreas073_c_94019" FBIS-EAS-94-073 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 North Korea Meets With Russian Guests Meets With Russian Guests SK1504045594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0442 GMT 15 Apr 94 SK1504045594 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 15 (KCNA) -- Secretary of the C.C. [Central Committee], the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] Hwang Chang-yop Thursday met and conversed in a friendly atmosphere with A. D. Vengerovsky, vice-chairman of the Liberal Democratic Party and deputy speaker of the state Duma of the Federation Council of Russia, and his entourage. Chi Chae-yong, vice-director of a department of the WPK Central Committee, was on hand.
